show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Betrayed by her husband Martin and backstabbed by his mistress Aleen, Sharon, once dismissed as a housewife, reveals her true identity as Musset, the legendary designer and the hidden CEO of MF, the world’s biggest fashion empire. But now that Sharon is the one closing billion-dollar deals, what happens to Martin? Will she make him regret ever cheating on her, or will she walk away from the pain and return to the man who broke her?
